# ActiveCampaign MCP Server — Environment Variables

# Required: Your ActiveCampaign API URL
# Format: https://YOURACCOUNTNAME.api-us1.com/api/3
# Find it in: Settings → Developer → API Access → URL
AC_API_URL=https://youraccountname.api-us1.com/api/3

# Required: Your ActiveCampaign API Key
# Find it in: Settings → Developer → API Access → Key
AC_API_KEY=your_api_key_here
